{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.length","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/length","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><em><code>length</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>removeItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>setItem()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Storage API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a> インターフェイスの読み取り専用プロパティ <code>length</code> は、<code>Storage</code> オブジェクトに保存されているデータアイテムの数を表す整数を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>aLength</em> = <em>storage</em>.length;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>整数</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の関数はカレントドメインのローカルストレージに 3 個のデータアイテムを追加して、ストレージ内のアイテムの数を返します:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'yellow'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Helvetica'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'cats.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 3 を返す</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>注記</strong>: 実際の例として、<a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/web-storage-demo\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage Demo</a> をご覧ください。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">策定状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"about:unknown#dom-storage-length\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"ja\">length の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-\">不明</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Storage.length","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/length/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API を使用する</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Storage インターフェイスの読み取り専用プロパティ length は、Storage オブジェクトに保存されているデータアイテムの数を表す整数を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Storage.length","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/storage/length","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/storage/length/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri